					<description><![CDATA[Hướng dẫn kích hoạt Microsoft Remote Desktop Licensing Xin chào các bạn, hôm nay mình sẽ hướng dẫn các bạn cách cài đặt và kích hoạt Microsoft Remote Desktop Licensing Bài viết này sẽ hướng dẫn từng bước một cách cài đặt license server, kích hoạt và thêm license để sử dụng cho Remote Desktop <a class="more-link" href="./../../../huong-dan-kich-hoat-microsoft-remote-desktop-licensing/index.html">Read More ...</a>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a class="a2a_button_facebook" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=.%2F%2Fhuong-dan-kich-hoat-microsoft-remote-desktop-licensing%2F&amp;linkname=H%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng%20d%E1%BA%ABn%20k%C3%ADch%20ho%E1%BA%A1t%20Microsoft%20Remote%20Desktop%20Licensing" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_twitter" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=.%2F%2Fhuong-dan-kich-hoat-microsoft-remote-desktop-licensing%2F&amp;linkname=H%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng%20d%E1%BA%ABn%20k%C3%ADch%20ho%E1%BA%A1t%20Microsoft%20Remote%20Desktop%20Licensing" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_email" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/email?linkurl=.%2F%2Fhuong-dan-kich-hoat-microsoft-remote-desktop-licensing%2F&amp;linkname=H%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng%20d%E1%BA%ABn%20k%C3%ADch%20ho%E1%BA%A1t%20Microsoft%20Remote%20Desktop%20Licensing" title="Email" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_dd a2a_counter addtoany_share_save addtoany_share" href="https://www.addtoany.com/share#url=.%2F%2Fhuong-dan-kich-hoat-microsoft-remote-desktop-licensing%2F&#038;title=H%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng%20d%E1%BA%ABn%20k%C3%ADch%20ho%E1%BA%A1t%20Microsoft%20Remote%20Desktop%20Licensing" data-a2a-url="./../../../huong-dan-kich-hoat-microsoft-remote-desktop-licensing/index.html" data-a2a-title="Hướng dẫn kích hoạt Microsoft Remote Desktop Licensing"></a></p><p><span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong>Hướng dẫn kích hoạt Microsoft Remote Desktop Licensing</strong></span></p>
<p>Xin chào các bạn, hôm nay mình sẽ hướng dẫn các bạn cách cài đặt và kích hoạt Microsoft Remote Desktop Licensing</p>
<p>Bài viết này sẽ hướng dẫn từng bước một cách cài đặt license server, kích hoạt và thêm license để sử dụng cho Remote Desktop Session Host (RDSH)</p>
<p><span style="color: #ff0000;">Lưu ý: Bài hướng dẫn này hướng đến mục tiêu môi trường giáo dục và thử nghiệm. Các bạn không được dùng trong môi trường doanh nghiệp hoặc thương mại</span></p>
<p><strong>1 &#8211; Cài đặt máy chủ Remote Desktop Licensing:</strong></p>
<p>Trong bài này mình dùng Windows Server 2012 R2, các bạn có thể dùng các bản cũ hơn như Windows Server 2012 hoặc Windows Server 2008 R2. Bản mới nhất sẽ bao gồm license luôn cho các bản còn lại.</p>
<p>Để cài đặt Remote Desktop Licensing các bạn mở Server Manager và chọn Add Roles and Features Wizard.</p>
<p>Chọn <span style="color: #993366;">Role based or features based installation</span> và Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-1.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1123" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-1-620x345.png" alt="Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-1" width="620" height="345" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-1-620x345.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-1-920x512.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-1.png 1058w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn máy chủ để cài đặt Role, do có 1 máy chủ nên đã được chọn sẵn. Click Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-2.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1124" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-2-620x438.png" alt="Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-2" width="620" height="438" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-2-620x438.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-2.png 801w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Phần Server Roles chọn <span style="color: #993366;">Remote Desktop Services</span> và Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-3.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1125" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-3-620x438.png" alt="Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-3" width="620" height="438" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-3-620x438.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-3.png 801w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Bỏ qua phần Feature và click Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-4.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1126" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-4-620x438.png" alt="Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-4" width="620" height="438" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-4-620x438.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-4.png 801w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-5.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1127" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-5-620x438.png" alt="Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-5" width="620" height="438" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-5-620x438.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-5.png 801w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Phần Role Services chọn <span style="color: #993366;">Remote Desktop Licensing</span> và click Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-6.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1128" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-6-620x438.png" alt="Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-6" width="620" height="438" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-6-620x438.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-6.png 801w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Xác nhận các thông tin trước khi cài đặt, click Install để tiến hành cài đặt</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-7.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1129" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-7-620x438.png" alt="Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-7" width="620" height="438" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-7-620x438.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-7.png 801w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Cài đặt hoàn tất</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-8.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1130" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-8-620x438.png" alt="Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-8" width="620" height="438" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-8-620x438.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Install-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-8.png 801w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p><strong>2 &#8211; Kích hoạt máy chủ Remote Desktop License</strong></p>
<p>Để sử dụng máy chủ License chúng ta cần kích hoạt máy chủ. Máy cần kết nối Internet để tiến hành kích hoạt</p>
<p>Để tiến hành kích hoạt chúng ta mở Control Panel =&gt; Administrative Tools =&gt; Remote Desktop Services =&gt; RD License Manager</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-1.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1131" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-1-620x455.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-1" width="620" height="455" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-1-620x455.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-1.png 801w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Click chuột phải vào server và chọn Properties</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-2.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1132" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-2-620x329.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-2" width="620" height="329" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-2-620x329.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-2.png 794w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Ở tab <span style="color: #993366;">Connection Method</span> chúng ta chọn là Web Browser</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-3.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1133" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-3-620x365.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-3" width="620" height="365" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-3-620x365.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-3.png 794w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Điền các thông tin yêu cầu vào tab <span style="color: #993366;">Required Information</span> =&gt; OK</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-4.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1134" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-4-620x365.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-4" width="620" height="365" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-4-620x365.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-4.png 794w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Chuột phải vào server và chọn <span style="color: #993366;">Activate server</span> để tiến hành kích hoạt máy chủ</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-5.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1135" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-5-620x365.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-5" width="620" height="365" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-5-620x365.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-5.png 794w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Một hộp thoại xuất hiện, click Next để bắt đầu.</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-6.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1136" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-6.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-6" width="565" height="626" /></a></p>
<p>Connection Method, chọn Web Browser</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-7.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1137" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-7.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-7" width="565" height="626" /></a></p>
<p>Để tiến hành click vào đường link trong hộp thoại, một cửa sổ web sẽ mở ra</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-8.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1138" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-8.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-8" width="565" height="626" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn ngôn ngữ (English) và check chọn Activate a license server =&gt; Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-9.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1139" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-9-620x338.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-9" width="620" height="338" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-9-620x338.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-9-920x501.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-9.png 1125w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Copy và paste Product ID, nhập tên công ty và quốc gia =&gt; Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-10.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1140" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-10-620x338.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-10" width="620" height="338" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-10-620x338.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-10-920x501.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-10.png 1125w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Review lại thông tin và Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-11.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1141" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-11-620x338.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-11" width="620" height="338" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-11-620x338.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-11-920x501.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-11.png 1125w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Kích hoạt thành công, copy chuỗi mã kích hoạt</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-12.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1142" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-12-620x338.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-12" width="620" height="338" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-12-620x338.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-12-920x501.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-12.png 1125w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Dán chuỗi mã kích hoạt vào hộp thoại và click Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-13.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1143" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-13.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-13" width="565" height="626" /></a></p>
<p>Hoàn tất kích hoạt máy chủ Remote Desktop License</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-14.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1144" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-14.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Server-14" width="565" height="626" /></a></p>
<p><strong>3 &#8211; Thêm bản quyền cho máy chủ Remote Desktop License</strong></p>
<p>Sau khi đã kích hoạt máy chủ bản quyền thành công, chúng ta tiến hành thêm bản quyền cho máy chủ này.</p>
<p>Click chuột phải vào máy chủ license và chọn<span style="color: #993366;"> Install Licenses</span></p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-1.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1145" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-1-620x310.png" alt="Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-1" width="620" height="310" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-1-620x310.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-1-920x460.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-1.png 936w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Một hộp thoại xuất hiện, click Next để tiếp tục</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-2.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1146" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-2.png" alt="Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-2" width="565" height="626" /></a></p>
<p>Click vào đường link trong hộp thoại, một cửa sổ web sẽ hiện ra</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-3.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1147" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-3.png" alt="Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-3" width="565" height="626" /></a></p>
<p>Chọn ngôn ngữ (English) và check chọn <span style="color: #993366;">Install Client Access Licenses</span> và click Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-4.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1148" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-4-620x338.png" alt="Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-4" width="620" height="338" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-4-620x338.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-4-920x501.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-4.png 1125w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Dán license server id, tên công ty và quốc gia</p>
<p>Chọn License Program là Other (*)</p>
<p>Click Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-5.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1149" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-5-620x347.png" alt="Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-5" width="620" height="347" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-5-620x347.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-5-920x515.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-5.png 1040w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Product type chọn Remote Desktop Services (Per device hoặc per user nếu muốn)<br />
Nhập số lượng license vào mục Qualtity<br />
Agreement number nhập 6565792 (*)</p>
<p>Click Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-6.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1150" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-6-620x347.png" alt="Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-6" width="620" height="347" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-6-620x347.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-6-920x515.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-6.png 1040w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Review lại thông tin trước khi click Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-7.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1151" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-7-620x376.png" alt="Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-7" width="620" height="376" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-7-620x376.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-7-920x557.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-7.png 1040w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Kích hoạt thành công, copy dòng mã</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-8.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1152" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-8-620x376.png" alt="Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-8" width="620" height="376" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-8-620x376.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-8-920x557.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-8.png 1040w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Paste dòng mã đã copy vào hộp thoại như ảnh và click Next</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-9.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1153" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-9.png" alt="Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-9" width="565" height="626" /></a></p>
<p>Đã hoàn thành việc thêm license</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-10.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1154" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-10.png" alt="Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-10" width="565" height="626" /></a></p>
<p>Lặp lại tương tự các bước trên cho các phiên bản Windows Server 2008, 2003 nếu muốn.</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-11.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1155" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-11-620x297.png" alt="Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-11" width="620" height="297" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-11-620x297.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-11-920x441.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Remote-Desktop-Licensing-Add-License-11.png 976w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p><strong>4 &#8211; Kích hoạt Remote Desktop Services</strong></p>
<p>Sau khi đã có máy chủ license đang vận hành, chúng ta tiến hành kích hoạt cho Remote Desktop Services.</p>
<p>Trong bài mình cài Remote Desktop Session Host chung với máy chủ license nên trong bài mình dùng localhost, nếu các bạn cài đặt khác server thì phải dùng địa chỉ IP máy license server</p>
<p>Ảnh dưới là cửa sổ RD License Diagnoser khi chưa kích hoạt. Cụ thể là Remote Desktop Services chưa kết nối được với máy chủ bản quyền</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-1.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1156" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-1-620x345.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-1" width="620" height="345" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-1-620x345.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-1-920x512.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-1.png 1058w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Để cập nhật máy chủ bản quyền cho Remote Desktop Service, chúng ta cần chỉnh một vài tùy chọn trong Group Policy</p>
<p>Chạy lệnh <span style="color: #993366;">Run =&gt; gpedit.msc</span></p>
<p>Local Computer Policy =&gt; Computer Configuration =&gt; Administrative Templates =&gt; Windows Components =&gt; Remote Desktop Services =&gt; Remote Desktop Session Host =&gt; Licensing</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-2.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1157" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-2-620x345.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-2" width="620" height="345" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-2-620x345.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-2-920x512.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-2.png 1058w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p><span style="color: #993366;">Use the specified Remote Desktop License servers</span></p>
<p>Nhập IP máy chủ bản quyền vào và OK</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-3.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1158" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-3-620x345.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-3" width="620" height="345" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-3-620x345.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-3-920x512.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-3.png 1058w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p><span style="color: #993366;">Select the remote desktop licensing mode</span></p>
<p>Các bạn có thể tùy chọn Per device hoặc per user (tương ứng với máy chủ bản quyền) và OK</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-4.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1159" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-4-620x345.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-4" width="620" height="345" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-4-620x345.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-4-920x512.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-4.png 1058w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Cập nhật Group Policy</p>
<p>Chạy lệnh Run =&gt; <span style="color: #993366;">gpupdate /force</span></p>
<p>Khởi động lại máy, RD Licensing Diagnoser báo như ảnh dưới.</p>
<p><a href="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-5.png" rel="lightbox[1122]"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1160" src="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-5-620x345.png" alt="Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-5" width="620" height="345" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-5-620x345.png 620w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-5-920x512.png 920w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Activate-Remote-Desktop-Session-Host-5.png 1058w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px" /></a></p>
<p>Vậy là chúng ta đã hoàn tất việc kích hoạt cho máy chủ Remote Desktop Services.</p>
<p><span style="color: #993366;">(*)</span></p>
<p>Phần license program các bạn phải chọn đúng mới có thể kích hoạt được</p>
<p>Mình bổ sung một số license program và agreement number như bên dưới, các bạn có thể thử nếu muốn</p>
<blockquote><p>License program: Select License<br />
Agreement number: 3647589</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>License program: Other</p>
<p>Agreement number: 6565792</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>License program: Select License</p>
<p>Agreement number: 4965437</p></blockquote>
